<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/20587318">觉得自己没有梦想或理想的时候该怎么办？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="415343" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">是不是照样可以活得很好？</div>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-meta zm-item-comment-el clearfix" id="zh-question-meta-wrap">
